{"tid":1118795,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有乘客指疑最後的巴士收掣不及致五巴士相撞","createTime":"2019-04-21T14:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T14:26:27.000Z","uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c31867653ffc8da50ed7ced1e30460afa7f0970f","tid":1118795,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T14:26:27.000Z","msg":"青馬大橋往機場方向五輛巴士相撞，三十八人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的五輛巴士車頭及車尾損毀，玻璃碎裂，有巴士車門飛脫，掉在馬路上。<br />\n<br />\n事發在下午四時許，青馬大橋往機場方向，兩輛城巴、兩輛龍運及一輛旅遊巴在大橋中段相撞。<br />\n<br />\n警方及救護員到場協助傷者及乘客下車，傷者坐在路邊等候分流，有人要由擔架床送上救護車。<br />\n<br />\n有乘客指懷疑最後的巴士收掣不及導致意外。<br />\n<br />\n受車禍影響，警方一度封閉兩條行車線，現場交通一度擠塞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=345275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D345275&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RBw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=62905995\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D345275&h=8282ab9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=345275</a>"}]}